Description: Mud model of a grain silo.
Excavator/field collector: Excavated by: Dr David George Hogarth
Curator's comments: Mentioned by Hogarth as standing on the head end of a coffin. Zitman notes it as marked with 'IX'.
Bibliographic references: Zitman 2010 / The necropolis of Assiut: a case study of local Egyptian funerary culture from the Old Kingdom to the end of the Middle Kingdom (I, 172, n.1147)
